#   Priority 2: Config-file TenantOverrides in GovernanceOptions
#   Priority 3: GovernanceOptions.Defaults
#
# The requests below use EXISTING endpoints to demonstrate that
# governance policies now resolve per-tenant at runtime.
#   - AE1: Create tenant for governance testing
#   - AE2: Set AllowedTools override for tenant
#   - AE3: Set TokenBudget override for tenant
#   - AE4: Verify resolved config reflects overrides
#   - AE5: Triage with tenant-specific governance → allowed tools apply
#   - AE6: Triage without tenant → governance defaults apply
###########################################################################

@tenantAE_name = acme-governance-29

