###############################################################################
# AP — Pack Evidence Observability & Correlation (Slice 42)
#
# Slice 42 adds structured telemetry (System.Diagnostics.Metrics counters)
# and end-to-end CorrelationId propagation to the pack evidence execution
# pipeline.  Nine counters under the "OpsCopilot.Packs" meter track every
# gate and query outcome — attempt, skip, workspace-resolution-failure,
# collector success/failure/truncation, and query blocked/timeout/failure.
#
# The CorrelationId supplied in alertPayload.correlationId now flows through
# the entire evidence path and appears in every counter tag plus structured
# log scopes, enabling distributed-trace correlation across triage calls.
#
# Scenario matrix:
#   AP1 — ModeB with correlationId  → correlationId echoed in evidence results
#   AP2 — ModeB without correlationId → system generates one (non-null results)
#   AP3 — ModeC with correlationId   → multi-pack evidence correlation
#   AP4 — ModeA triage               → evidence skipped, telemetry only
###############################################################################

