### ================================================================
### AU. Pack SafeAction Definition Validation + Preview (Dev Slice 51)
### ================================================================
###
### Dev Slice 51: Additive-only, Recommend-Only — Adds three new nullable
###   fields to each PackSafeActionProposalDto item inside
###   packSafeActionProposals[]:
###     definitionValidationErrorCode — kebab-case error code or null
###     definitionValidationMessage   — human-readable error or null
###     operatorPreview               — deterministic Operator Card text or null
###
### Validation runs a frozen minimal-schema check (12 error codes).
### Operator Card is a deterministic multi-line text block:
###   == Operator Card ==
###   Action : {displayName}
###   Type   : {actionType}
###   Params : {sorted keys} | (none) | (parse error)
###   Valid  : yes | no — {errorCode}: {errorMessage}
###
### Fields are null when:
###   - Mode A (proposals not generated at all)
###   - Packs:SafeActionsEnabled = false (proposals not generated)
###   - DefinitionFile is null/absent for that action
###
### Test cases:
###   AU1 — ModeB triage: validation fields present on proposals (happy path)
###   AU2 — ModeC triage: operatorPreview contains Operator Card text
###   AU3 — ModeB triage: DTO shape — all 3 new fields present on each proposal
###   AU4 — ModeA triage: proposals absent, validation fields not applicable
###   AU5 — Feature disabled: proposals absent, validation fields not applicable
###   AU6 — ModeB triage: multiple proposals — each has independent validation
###############################################################################

### AU1 — ModeB triage: validation fields present on proposals (happy path)
# Expected: 200 OK.  Each item in packSafeActionProposals[] includes:
#   definitionValidationErrorCode — null if the definition is well-formed
#   definitionValidationMessage   — null if the definition is well-formed
#   operatorPreview               — non-null multi-line Operator Card string
#     containing "== Operator Card ==" header and "Valid  : yes"
# Items without a definitionFile will have all three fields as null.
# NOTE: Server must be in Mode B or C (Packs:DeploymentMode ≥ "B") with
#   Packs:SafeActionsEnabled = true.
# @name triageModeB_ValidationFieldsHappyPath
POST {{baseUrl}}/agent/triage
Content-Type: application/json
x-tenant-id: {{tenantId}}

{
